OL,7,FAt a music class for young children in
OL,8,FThornhill, Michael Ansell, a board
OL,9,Fmember of Gaelic language committee
OL,10,FGaidhlig DumGal, suggested the
OL,11,Flanguage was part of the history and
OL,12,Fculture of the area.
