OL,7,FIn a statement Councillor Maureen
OL,8,FJohnstone, Chair of Dumfries and
OL,9,FGalloway Council's Education, Skills
OL,10,Fand Community Wellbeing Committee,
OL,11,Fsaid: "We are delighted to be working
OL,12,Fwith voluntary group Gaelic DumGal and
OL,13,Flocal partners to help promote a range
OL,14,Fof activities that will be available
OL,15,Fduring World Gaelic Week."
