OL,7,FChair of Gaidhlig DumGal, Eilidh
OL,8,FScammell, said: "Gaidhlig DumGal is a
OL,9,Fvoluntary organisation dedicated to
OL,10,Fpromoting our Gaelic heritage and
OL,11,Flanguage learning here in Dumfries and
OL,12,FGalloway.
OL,14,F"Our Gaelic heritage is written in our
OL,15,Fplace-names and personal names right
OL,16,Facross the region and we are delighted
OL,17,Fto be participating with the local
OL,18,FCouncil and Bord na Gaidhlig in the
OL,19,Fprogramme for Seachdain na Gaidhlig
OL,20,FWorld Gaelic Week."
